> # Show ts generate subcommand help
> composio ts generate --help
composio

composio 0.1.24

USAGE

$ generate [(-o, --output-dir directory)] [--compact] [--transpiled] [--type-tools]
 --toolkits text...

DESCRIPTION

Generate TypeScript types for toolkits, tools, and triggers from the Composio API.

Environment Variables:
  COMPOSIO_TOOLKIT_VERSION_<TOOLKIT>  Override toolkit version (e.g., COMPOSIO_TOOL
KIT_VERSION_GMAIL=20250901_00)
                                      Use "latest" or unset to use the latest versi
on.

OPTIONS

(-o, --output-dir directory)

  A directory.

  Output directory for the generated TypeScript type stubs.

  This setting is optional.

--compact

  A true or false value.

  Emit a single TypeScript file

────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
